        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="阳明四句教"><a href="#阳明四句教" class="headerlink" title="阳明四句教"></a>阳明四句教</h1><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>😄</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f604.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span></p><p>无善无恶心之体，有善有恶意之动，知善知恶是良知，为善去恶是格物。</p><p>无声无臭独知时，此是乾坤万有基。抛却自家无尽藏，沿门持钵效贫儿。</p><p><img src="https://ss2.meipian.me/users/9908934/originf2d8b1771217ab56e7acb89e7fa7236c.jpg-mobile" alt="图片"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
